HEADWORD: Subtribe
<hw>Sub"tribe`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot. &
Zool.)</fld> <def>A division of a tribe; a group of genera of a little
lower rank than a tribe.</def>⟦br⟧
